Package org.soulwing.prospecto.api

Interface ViewEntity

  • public interface ViewEntity
    An abstract entity in a view.

    An instance of this type is used collect the properties of an entity associated with a node of type object or array-of-objects until an instance of the model type associated with the node can be instantiated.

    Author:
    Carl Harris

        void put​(String name,
         Object value)
        Replaces a property value.

        Any existing value associated with name is replaced by value.

        This method cannot be used to add new property to the entity.

        Parameters:

        value - the value to set
